<p><a name="External_links" id="External_links"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Irenaeus&amp;action=edit&amp;section=16" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.earlychristianwritings.com/irenaeus.html" class="external text" title="http://www.earlychristianwritings.com/irenaeus.html" rel="nofollow">Early Christian Writings Irenaeus</a> (inaccessible, presumably since September 9, 2008)(is again available as of 23MAR09)</li>
